WEBVTT

00:06:29.840 --> 00:06:32.856
But the problem is
they're very fragmented.

00:06:32.880 --> 00:06:35.200
Think about how many profiles you have.

00:06:36.520 --> 00:06:42.016
Blockchains allow for us
to create an open, global platform

00:06:42.040 --> 00:06:46.416
on which to store any attestation
about any individual

00:06:46.440 --> 00:06:47.840
from any source.

00:06:48.480 --> 00:06:51.776
This allows us to create a user-controlled

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:53.160
portable identity.

00:06:55.800 --> 00:06:57.696
More than a profile,

00:06:57.720 --> 00:07:01.016
it means you can selectively reveal